node.text:
This full-flared long skirt in super-fine nappa leather has a flowing effect from the high waist to the ankles. It is worn with an extra-long, crochet winter scarf featuring hand-inserted fringes and the low-heeled Edith winter boot in vegetal calfskin

Discover the Chloé Autumn-Winter 2021 collection in boutiques and on chloe.com

#CHLOE

For her #ChloeAW21 debut, Gabriela Hearst introduces the Chloé Puffcho, a traditional poncho reinterpreted as a striped cashmere blanket with a puffer-jacket insert in recycled eco-nylon. It is worn with an Edith Collector bag handcrafted from leftover wool and cashmere

Discover the Chloé Autumn-Winter 2021 collection in boutiques and on chloe.com

#CHLOE
